        <scopecontent id="ref1">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>One scrapbook (66 pp.) compiled by Abraham Skolnik of memorabilia from the Spanish Civil War, titled "Welcome Home Veterans of the Abraham Lincoln Brigade!" It contains newspaper and periodical clippings, photographs of individual veterans and of Spanish scenes, and ephemera.</p>
